{"tid":1509454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地區行動其實係咪應該停一停","createTime":"2019-08-27T00:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:44:43.000Z","uid":197777,"like":14,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"24bb970787635bb85f674627125f4f1a8a0fac2b","tid":1509454,"uid":197777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:22:35.000Z","msg":"最初2014年佔領無用<br />\n到2次百萬大遊行無用 <br />\n就開始有地區行動 <br />\n持續左2個幾月<br />\n除左幾百個人比人拉 <br />\n無數人受傷<br />\n2邊武力升級<br />\n一邊雞尾<br />\n一邊開始拔槍 水炮<br />\n大佬啊點升級都無可能夠對面黎 對面幾乎係無上限 無限金錢 核彈都唔割 唔代表你真係有核彈<br />\n繼續落去除左更多人比人拉 之外真係睇唔到有咩突破 唔通各位真係要因衝突死左第一個人先識諗<br />\n<br />\n開始停一停 諗下 遊行 地區行動 以外既出路<br />\n<br />\n我知一定比人屌做分化 失敗主義 冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n自問我只不過係一個超合理 理性主義者<br />\n<br />\n從來都一考慮所有野都一定以成本效益優先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從一開始就覺得遊行係最無撚用所以一次都無去由其民陣果d</span><br />\n<br />\n本身覺得地區行動可能會有用 但2個月黎 結果有目共睹 所以有感而發 出呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dcd9abb59129a6d23417fbda85f120ccc1575b","tid":1509454,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=812f226e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=e82f77c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgzu